\c 2
\s Abazalwane balaywa ukuthi bangabandlululi abantu
\p
\v 1 Bazalwane bami, kungeyisikho ngokubandlulula abantu libe lokholo\x + Mark. 11.22.\x* lweNkosi yethu uJesu Kristu, \add iNkosi\add* yenkazimulo\x + 1 Kor. 2.8. Seb. 7.2.\x*\x + 2.9. Dute. 1.17; 10.17. & Zaga 24.23; 2 Kor. 5.16. 1 Pet. 1.17. Juda 1.16.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba uba kungena emhlanganweni\f + \fk emhlanganweni: \fl kumbe, \fq esinagogeni.\f* wenu indoda elendandatho yegolide lesembatho esikhazimulayo\x + 2.3. Luka 23.11.\x*, besekungena longumyanga olesembatho esingcolileyo,
\v 3 beselinanzelela\x + Luka 1.48.\x* ogqoke isembatho esikhazimulayo\x + 2.3. Luka 23.11.\x* beselisithi kuye: Wena hlala lapha kuhle; beselisithi kongumyanga\x + Zaga 18.23.\x*: Wena mana lapho, loba: Hlala lapha ngaphansi kwesenabelo senyawo zami;
\v 4 pho, kalibandlululi phakathi kwenu\x + 3.17. Mat. 21.21.\x*\x + Roma 14.1.\x*, njalo laba ngabahluleli abalemicabango emibi yini?\x + Mat. 15.19.\x*\x + Roma 14.1.\x*
\v 5 Zwanini, bazalwane bami abathandekayo. UNkulunkulu kabakhethanga\x + Efe. 1.4.\x*\x + 1 Kor. 1.27,28. Jobe 34.19.\x* yini abayanga balumhlaba, benothile ekholweni\x + Zaga 13.7. 2 Kor. 8.9. Isam. 2.9. Luka 12.21.\x*, njalo bezindlalifa\x + Mat. 25.34.\x* zombuso\x + Mat. 5.3. Luka 6.20; 12.32.\x* awuthembisayo\x + 1.12.\x* kwabamthandayo\x + Eks. 20.6. 1 Kor. 2.9. Zaga 8.17. 2 Tim. 4.8.\x*?
\v 6 Kodwa lina libadumazile abayanga\x + 5.6. 1 Kor. 11.22.\x*. Abanothileyo kabalicindezeli yini, njalo akusibo yini abalidonsela\x + Seb. 16.19.\x* ekwahlulelweni?\x + 5.6. Seb. 8.3; 13.50; 17.6; 18.12.\x*
\v 7 Bona kabalihlambazi\x + 1 Tim. 6.1. 1 Pet. 4.14. Seb. 13.45.\x* yini ibizo elihle elibizwa ngalo\x + Seb. 15.17.\x*?
